<html lang='en' dir='ltr'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <meta name='color-scheme' content='light' />
    <meta name='supported-color-schemes' content='light' />
    <title>Welcome to Ignite Connections</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;
      color: #292929; background-color: #fafafa; } .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0
      auto; background-color: #ffffff; } .header { padding: 30px 40px 10px; } .logo { max-width:
      175px; height: auto; display: block; } .welcome-title { color: #292929; font-size: 24px;
      margin: 10px 0 10px 0; padding-top: 10px; } .content { padding: 0 40px; } .content p {
      margin:5px; } h1 { color: #292929; font-size: 24px; text-align: left; margin: 8px 0; }
      .button-container { text-align: center; padding: 5px 0; } .button { display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 10px; background-color: #1c3494; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 14px; margin-top:
      5px; } .button:hover { background-color: #0056b3; } .campaign-section { background-color:
      #f0f7ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; }
      .important-notes { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px
      0; } .important-notes h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0; color: #333333; } ul {
      padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0; } li { margin-bottom: 10px; } .footer { text-align:
      center; padding: 20px; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      margin-top: 20px; } @media screen and (max-width: 600px) { .content { padding: 0 20px; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <img
          src='https://realqualified.dev.coditas.org/assets/image/brand_logo.png'
          alt='Ignite Connections Logo'
          width='175'
          class='logo'
        />
        <h1 class='welcome-title'>Welcome to Ignite Connections</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <p><strong>Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</strong></p>

        <p>
          We received a request to reset your password for the
          <strong>Ignite Connections Admin Portal. </strong>
          If you made this request, please click the button below to reset your password:
        </p>

        <div class='button-container'>
          <a href={{resetPasswordLink}} class='button'>Reset Password</a>
        </div>

        <div class='important-notes'>
          <h2>Important Notes:</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              This link is valid for
              <strong>15 minutes.</strong>
            </li>
            <li>
              If you did not request a password reset, you can ignore this email.
            </li>
            <li>
              For security reasons, do not share this link with anyone.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>If you need further assistance, please contact support.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>The Ignite Connections Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>